    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, offering a dependable driving experience for its next owner. While the exterior shows some minor cosmetic signs of regular use, such as small stone chips on the hood, the paint still holds a great shine. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It is a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles.",
