    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in pristine, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and free of any cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers an unparalleled driving experience for the most discerning buyer. This is an investment-grade example, preserved with absolute care and ready for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 43500.0,
